        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊談判有方案 油價明顯急跌 恒指望企25600｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L7I1oEqoJQCHE7eLn0VKcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/bab35f35cd34ffe468f46ff7760cb915\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><ol class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長假期間，美伊局勢反覆，但最終停戰方案出爐，而特朗普在指伊朗文明將消滅後，又再推遲限期。美伊和談有曙光，特別是海峽通行方案，令油價大幅下跌，全球股市有望急彈。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股盤前走勢不錯，雖然難收復所有戰前跌幅，但資金仍然活躍，不過相對來說港股更值博。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股方面，AI大模型股及航空股都有上揚空間，而原油航運需求更大，預計亦有水位可炒。至於傳統板塊則值博率一般。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">指數方面，預計恆指上望26000，支持位25600點，26500點及26800點有較大阻力。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恆指牛熊證街貨，牛證比例與熊證接近，大戶夾熊後再看熊證反應。</p></li></ol></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9B%E4%BC%8125600-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000493.html",
