            "title": "國際｜伊朗：霍爾木茲海峽兩星期內將實現安全通航",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜伊朗：霍爾木茲海峽兩星期內將實現安全通航\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜伊朗：<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>兩星期內將實現安全通航</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外交部長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"阿拉格齊\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:阿拉格齊;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿拉格齊\">阿拉格齊</a>在當地星期三凌晨，代表伊朗最高國家安全委員會宣布，霍爾木茲海峽將於兩星期時間內，實現安全通航。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿拉格齊說，作為對巴基斯坦方面請求的回應，他宣布如果美國及以色列停止對伊朗的襲擊，伊朗武裝部隊將停止反擊，在與伊朗武裝部隊協調的前提下，未來兩星期船隻將能在技術限制允許的前提下，安全通過霍爾木茲海峽。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97-%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%85%A9%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E5%85%A7%E5%B0%87%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%80%9A%E8%88%AA-012713653.html",
